      <title>#185 - A Conversation with Paul Bloom</title>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2020 20:19:43 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">1521089</guid>
      <link>https://samharris.org/subscriber-extras/185-february-7-2020/</link>
      <itunes:subtitle/>
      <description><![CDATA[In this episode of the podcast, Sam Harris and Paul Bloom speak about "Trump Derangement Syndrome," inequality, the relationship between wealth and happiness, the downside of fame, psychological impediments to noticing progress, and other topics.

