      <description><![CDATA[In this episode of the Making Sense podcast, Sam Harris speaks with Johann Hari about his books <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1620408910/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=wwwsamharris03-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=1620408910&amp;linkId=186176a31405e6b5060c8681c5a1a7b0"><em>Chasing the Scream</em></a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/163286830X/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=wwwsamharris03-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=163286830X&amp;linkId=c392b71d43988525ae6b2b5a50248237"><em>Lost Connections</em></a>.

